SNo.ProblemDescription: AC1200 Wifi range extender; Tether app cannot find the device
SNo.SolutionDescription: Plug extender into a power outlet next to router; Detect device; Relocate halfway between Wifi router and weak zone

Pixma E470; Canon PRINT Inkjet/SELPHY app cannot find the printer
SNo.SolutionDescription: Getting Started 2; #2 Check the status of the Wi-Fi lamp on the printer; The lamp is flashing => #B Troubleshooting; Press Wi-Fi button and release it when Wi-Fi lamp flashes, press black button, press Wi-Fi button repeatedly until Network lamp lights, press Color button or Black button to finalize selection

https://support.usa.canon.com/library/ij/Manual/All/E470%20series/EN/NTR/bg-trouble1200.html; (cannot find printer using wireless LAN); #A, Check 2; Press Wi-Fi button and release it when Wi-Fi lamp flashes, press black button, press Wi-Fi button repeatedly until Network lamp lights, press Color button or Black button to finalize selection
